He may be a saboteur.

1291
01:20:05.119 --> 01:20:08.158
♪ Yeah it feels ♪

1292
01:20:08.159 --> 01:20:12.358
♪ So good I might
just lose my mind ♪

1293
01:20:12.359 --> 01:20:14.919
♪ No question if
