You pull that shit again. I
will knock your teeth out.

1358
01:24:11.840 --> 01:24:13.599
Oh. no one gets past us
without a fight. right?

1359
01:24:13.600 --> 01:24:15.679
Oh. is this funny? You think
you got a seat next year?

1360
