1369
01:24:44.319 --> 01:24:47.679
-Thanks. coach.
-Get your shit together!

1370
01:24:47.680 --> 01:24:50.319
So stupid! God...

1371
01:24:58.119 --> 01:24:59.519
How would you sum
up your race today?

1372
01:24:59.520 --> 01:25:02.358
Ooh. Um. it was good.

1373
01:25:02.359 --> 01:25:05.479
You know. the car feels great. I
think the team's done an amazing job.

1374
