- Of living in a van?

1412
01:27:19.960 --> 01:27:21.198
Total freedom.

1413
01:27:21.199 --> 01:27:22.279
Total failure.

1414
01:27:22.960 --> 01:27:24.559
Says the guy who still
lives with his mom.

1415
01:27:24.560 --> 01:27:25.999
Says the guy with two pair.

1416
