your fathers died?

1445
01:28:50.840 --> 01:28:51.799
Sorry.

1446
01:28:51.800 --> 01:28:53.079
- Thirteen.
- Thirteen.

1447
01:28:55.680 --> 01:28:57.119
Huh.

1448
01:28:58.119 --> 01:28:59.278
