Put the thing down. will ya?

1451
01:29:05.359 --> 01:29:07.158
What do you care what they say?

1452
01:29:07.159 --> 01:29:08.959
Easy for you to say.
They all love you.

1453
01:29:08.960 --> 01:29:10.239
It's just noise. man.

1454
01:29:11.720 --> 01:29:13.198
